Private Events
The Santa Fe Bar
The Santa Fe Bar, the perfect destination for private events. Our venue features a fully stocked bar, a private pool hall, and a fenced rear patio. For your safety and peace of mind, we offer security services upon request for an additional fee, ensuring your event runs smoothly and securely. Additionally, our fenced rear patio not only provides a private outdoor setting but also supports food truck access, allowing for a diverse and hassle-free dining experience.
Email for a quote and to book.
23731 South US Highway 441, High Springs, Florida 32643, United States
